&ldquo;Bale has been an idol for me since that game against Inter,&rdquo; he explained. &ldquo;Since that game in the Champions League I started to follow him, to watch YouTube videos of him and I became a big fan. I bought his shirts, his books &ndash; everything about him. <span class="red">And now being able to be here with him, in the club that raised him</span>&hellip;<span class="red"> I showed him on the plane the tweets that I wrote to him, and the pictures that I have from him</span>, and he enjoyed that! He told me that Tottenham is a top club &ndash; those were his words. He said that everything here is top. He praised the training ground, the players, everything. He didn&rsquo;t say a single negative thing about the club and at that moment I thought &lsquo;great!&rsquo;
